VoiceCallQualityFeedback.name: VoiceCallQualityFeedback
VoiceCallQualityFeedback.description: Represents feedback given by a Sales Dialer user about the quality of a VoiceCall .

FeedbackText.description: The detailed feedback about a call left by a user.

FeedbackType.description: The feedback category (Call could not connect, Audio lagged, etc.) selected by a user.

OwnerId.description: The ID of the user leaving the feedback.

VoiceCallId.description: The ID of the related VoiceCall.
